<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <span class="eyebrow">Restaurant POS</span>
                    <h1>Voice, AI, and IoT routing built for busy restaurant floors</h1>
                    <p>Bhojan Mitra keeps front-of-house, kitchen stations, and delivery channels in sync with conversational ordering, multilingual support, and real-time analytics.</p>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Explore pilot features</a>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Talk to the founders</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-meta">
                        <span>Pilot slots for 2025 rollout</span>
                        <span>Kitchen displays &amp; printers on our roadmap</span>
                        <span>Offline fallbacks in development</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </section>

        <section class="benefits">
            <div class="container">
                <span class="eyebrow">Operational wins</span>
                <h2>Designed for the realities of service</h2>
                <div class="benefits-list">
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h4>Faster table turns</h4>
                        <p>Voice call-outs route straight to the right station; no double entry or paper tickets during peak rush.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h4>Error-proof operations</h4>
                        <p>Modifiers, special requests, and allergen notes are highlighted automatically on KDS and printed tickets.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefit">
                        <h4>Staff confidence</h4>
                        <p>Multilingual prompts and guided flows help new team members pick up service routines quickly.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="features" class="features">
            <div class="container">
                <span class="eyebrow">Restaurant capabilities</span>
                <h2>Tools that keep your floor, kitchen, and delivery channels aligned</h2>
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Kitchen Display Integration</h3>
                        <p>Orders will appear at the correct station with colour-coded priority and prep timers — help us refine the flow during pilot runs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Table &amp; Order Management</h3>
                        <p>Voice-based table assignment, split bills, and mid-service modifications are being refined with partner floors.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Online &amp; Delivery Sync</h3>
                        <p>Consolidate delivery partners and in-house orders with voice confirmations so mismatched tickets are reduced.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Staff Productivity</h3>
                        <p>Use voice shortcuts for voids, comps, shift reports, and inventory pulls — without leaving the floor.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Run service the way your guests expect</h2>
                <p>Join the pilot to co-design voice-led ordering that matches your menu, service model, and hardware stack.</p>
                <div class="hero-actions center">
                    <a href="https://billing.aarohitavigyan.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Apply for a pilot walkthrough</a>
                    <a href="/pricing" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">View founding plans</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
